---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';
---
<Base
  title="1:1 Coaching — Body by Olga"
  description="Personalized strength coaching for women 40+. Apply to work directly with Olga and build real, lasting results."
  canonical="/coaching"
>
  <Nav activePage="coaching" />

  <!-- HERO -->
  <div class="sp">
    <div class="ctn">
      <div class="ch r">
        <h1>This isn't a program.<br/>It's a partnership.</h1>
        <p>Olga works with a small number of women at a time — closely, intentionally, with a level of attention that generic programs can't offer.</p>
        <p>If you're ready to do the work and want a coach who will actually know your name, your history, and your goals — this is where you apply.</p>
        <p class="note">Spots are limited. Olga takes on fewer than 10 new clients per month.</p>
        <a href="#" class="abtn">Apply for Coaching <span class="arr">→</span></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- WHAT YOU GET -->
  <section class="frame sp">
    <div class="ctn">
      <div class="frame-in r">
        <h2>What 1:1 coaching actually looks like.</h2>
        <p>This isn't you following a template and hoping it works. Olga builds a program around your body, your schedule, your history, and your goals — then adjusts it every week based on how you're actually doing.</p>
        <p>You'll meet weekly on video. You'll have direct messaging access between sessions. Your nutrition, your workouts, your sleep, your stress — all of it gets attention.</p>
        <p class="em">"The difference between knowing what to do and actually doing it is having someone in your corner."</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- COACHING WORKS FOR -->
  <section class="sp">
    <div class="ctn">
      <div class="cw r">
        <h2>This is for you if...</h2>
        <div class="cw-g">
          <div class="cw-c r d1">
            <h4>You're done with one-size-fits-all</h4>
            <p>You've tried programs that weren't built for you. You want something designed around your body, your hormones, your life.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="cw-c r d2">
            <h4>You want accountability</h4>
            <p>Knowing someone is waiting for your check-in changes everything. You're not just doing this alone.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="cw-c r d1">
            <h4>You're serious about results</h4>
            <p>You're willing to put in the work consistently. You want guidance on how to do it right, not just harder.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="cw-c r d2">
            <h4>You have specific goals</h4>
            <p>Whether it's weight loss, strength building, or just feeling like yourself again — you have a clear picture of what success looks like.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
  <section class="chow sp">
    <div class="ctn">
      <h2 class="r">How it works.</h2>
      <div class="chow-g">
        <div class="chow-c r d1">
          <div class="num">STEP 01</div>
          <h4>Apply</h4>
          <p>Fill out the application. Tell Olga about where you are, what you've tried, and what you're working toward.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="chow-c r d2">
          <div class="num">STEP 02</div>
          <h4>Discovery Call</h4>
          <p>If it looks like a good fit, you'll book a 30-minute call with Olga to talk through your goals and answer any questions.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="chow-c r d3">
          <div class="num">STEP 03</div>
          <h4>Custom Program</h4>
          <p>Olga builds your first month of training and nutrition guidance, tailored specifically to you.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="chow-c r d4">
          <div class="num">STEP 04</div>
          <h4>Weekly Check-Ins</h4>
          <p>Every week you connect with Olga to review progress, adjust the plan, and keep momentum.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- COACHING TESTIMONIALS -->
  <section class="sp">
    <div class="ctn">
      <div class="ct r">
        <h2>Clients on coaching.</h2>
        <div class="ct-g">
          <div class="ct-c r d1">
            <p class="ct-q">"Olga noticed things no other coach ever had. She adjusted my program three times in the first month."</p>
            <div class="ct-a">Rachel T.</div>
            <div class="ct-d">1:1 Coaching client, 8 months</div>
          </div>
          <div class="ct-c r d2">
            <p class="ct-q">"Having someone who actually knows my situation — my schedule, my stress levels, my history — is irreplaceable."</p>
            <div class="ct-a">Dana W.</div>
            <div class="ct-d">1:1 Coaching client, 14 months</div>
          </div>
          <div class="ct-c r d1">
            <p class="ct-q">"I applied skeptically. Six months later I deadlift more than I ever thought possible at 49."</p>
            <div class="ct-a">Karen S.</div>
            <div class="ct-d">1:1 Coaching client, 6 months</div>
          </div>
          <div class="ct-c r d2">
            <p class="ct-q">"The weekly check-ins changed everything. I stopped going through the motions and started actually progressing."</p>
            <div class="ct-a">Michelle B.</div>
            <div class="ct-d">1:1 Coaching client, 4 months</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FINAL CTA -->
  <section class="cf sp">
    <div class="ctn">
      <h2 class="r">Ready to apply?</h2>
      <p class="r d1">Spots are limited. If you're serious about this, don't wait.</p>
      <a href="#" class="abtn r d2">Apply for Coaching →</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Base>
